Page._content:
Copyright (c) 2012-2016 BIZ4X Team

# BIZ4X APP

![BIZ4X](/images/biz4x.svg "BIZ4X")

[https://www.biz4x.com](https://www.biz4x.com)

---


* Jade Teamplate
* CSSMin, Uglify
* Bunder JS, CSS HTML
* SVG, ImageMin, Real Favicon
* Angular, Webpack
* Coffee Script, Babel, TypeScripts
* Concat, Webpack, Phantom, Karma
* SASS/SCSS, LESS, Stylus
* BrowserSync

### Hng dn Ci mi Project 

Windows: Chy file `install.bat`

MAC/Ubuntu: Chy file `sh install.sh` 

### Hng dn Update

Windows: Chy file `update.bat`

MAC/Ubuntu: Chy file `sh update.sh` 

### Hng dn chi tit

Chy `node tool` sau  tin hnh lm theo hng dn ti link `http://localhost:1234/`

#### Bo Nguyn
